            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM16.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Granola Bowl</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Crunchy granola with yogurt, honey, and fresh fruits.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="lunch" class="menu-section">
        <h2>LUNCH</h2>
        <div class="menu-grid">
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM18.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Grilled Chicken Salad</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Grilled chicken breast on a bed of mixed greens, with balsamic dressing.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM22.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Club Sandwich</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Layered sandwich with turkey, bacon, lettuce, tomato, and mayo, served with fries.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM25.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Seafood Pasta</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Al dente pasta tossed with fresh seafood in a light garlic sauce.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM20.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Veggie Burger</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Plant-based burger patty with lettuce, tomato, and special sauce, served with fries.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM19.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Tom Yum Soup</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Spicy and sour Thai soup with shrimp, mushrooms, and fragrant herbs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM18.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Quiche Lorraine</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Savory tart filled with eggs, cream, bacon, and cheese.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="dinner" class="menu-section">
        <h2>DINNER</h2>
        <div class="menu-grid">
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM30.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Grilled Salmon</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Fresh salmon fillet grilled to perfection, served with steamed vegetables.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM28.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Beef Steak</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Juicy ribeye steak cooked to your liking, served with roasted potatoes and sauce.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM20.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Vegetarian Stir-Fry</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Crispy vegetables stir-fried in a savory soy-based sauce, served with rice.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM35.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Roast Lamb</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Slow-cooked lamb with garlic, rosemary, and a side of mashed potatoes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM26.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Shrimp Scampi</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Juicy shrimp sautéed in garlic butter, served with pasta or rice.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <div class="price">RM32.00</div>
                <h3 class="item-title">Duck Breast</h3>
                <p class="item-description">Seared duck breast served with a berry reduction and seasonal vegetables.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>


